com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Interface CacheStorage


  • public interface CacheStorage
    The system for cache handling. The persistent cache are stored in the Browser data directory in Cache folder. By default all Browsers use predefined data directory. You can find out where this directory is located using the BrowserPreferences.getDefaultChromiumDir() method.

    So, if Browser A and B have the same data directory, then they will access the cache of each other.

    If you need to configure each Browser to use unique cache storage which is not accessible for other Browser instances, you need to provide unique user data directory for each Browser instance. The user data directory path can be provided via configured BrowserContextParams.BrowserContextParams(String) object that must be passed into the Browser.Browser(BrowserContext) factory method.
    用于缓存处理的系统。持久性高速缓存存储在“高速缓存”文件夹中的“浏览器”数据目录中。默认情况下，所有浏览器都使用预定义的数据目录。您可以使用BrowserPreferences.getDefaultChromiumDir（）方法找出此目录的位置。因此，如果浏览器A和B具有相同的数据目录，则它们将访问彼此的缓存。如果需要将每个浏览器配置为使用其他浏览器实例无法访问的唯一缓存存储，则需要为每个浏览器实例提供唯一的用户数据目录。可以通过已配置的BrowserContextParams.BrowserContextParams（String）对象提供用户数据目录路径，该对象必须传递到Browser.Browser（BrowserContext）工厂方法中。

    • Method Detail

      • clearCache

        void clearCache()
        Clears cache data in Browser's user data directory. This method clears cache asynchronously, so when this method returns there's no guaranty that all cache data is cleared completely. To clear cache and get notification when cache data is cleared completely use the clearCache(com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.events.Callback) method.
        清除浏览器用户数据目录中的缓存数据。此方法以异步方式清除缓存，因此，当该方法返回时，无法保证完全清除了所有缓存数据。若要清除缓存并在完全清除缓存数据时获取通知，请使用clearCache（com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.events.Callback）方法。
